TABS
New tab: :tabnew
Swtich tab: :tabn/tabp or :gt
Close tab: :tabclose
For more: :help tabpage
-p flag for multiple files in different tabs

For operations on multiple lines
<C-v> or Ctrl+v => visual block mode
A"<Esc> => append "

Format or identing
gg
=G

Splitting screen
Horizontal:
Ctrl+w then v
Vertical
Ctrl+w then s
The above open the same file 

For different files
Horizontal split
vim -o file1 file2 file3 ..... 
:sp filename

Vertical split
vim -O file1 file2 file3 ...
:vsp filename or :vs filename

:edit filename


Multiple cursors
vim-multi-cursors
vim-visual-multi
https://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=4467

